    :::{.callout-tip collapse="true"}
    ## Solución


    ::: {#0d589a94 .cell execution_count=4}
    ``` {.julia .cell-code}
    f(x, y) = x^2+y^2<1 ? 10 : 0
    f(v) = f(v...)
    hcubature(f, [-1,-1], [1,1])
    ```

    ::: {.cell-output .cell-output-display execution_count=5}
    ```
    (31.41598951201623, 4.6813472010342655e-7)
