a.  $\int_0^2\int_0^{x/2} e^{x+y}\,dy\,dx$.

    :::{.callout-tip collapse="true"}
    ## Solución


    ::: {#c19651ae .cell execution_count=10}
    ``` {.julia .cell-code}
